   <ext_description linkend="Advanced_boundary_representation_arm.Advanced_brep_shape_representation">
				An <b>Advanced_brep_shape_representation</b> is a type of <b>Shape_representation</b> in which the representation items are specializations of manifold_solid_brep entities. These specializations differ from the more general B-rep in that they shall only use explicit geometric forms for their face and edge geometry. The face geometry is restricted to elementary surfaces, swept surfaces or B-spline surfaces.
			</ext_description>

